{"title":"醒着的树","authors":["郭献宝"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":2,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒着的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭献宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直以为树是睡着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像沉默的老者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像祖先的煤黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直以为树是睡着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在林间嬉戏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缠绕在树上的藤萝是我的秋千"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用力摇撼着树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而树始终沉默不语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直以为树是睡着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我成长爬出森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后的大树被我伐倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站立行走昂首前行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空旷的原野把我诱惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直以为树是睡着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果剩下最后一棵树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的旷野成了荒芜的沙漠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而唯一的树依然笔直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像最后的士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是醒着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而谁在沉睡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直以为树是睡着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是那沉默的年轮深刻的纹路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一圈又一圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才交织成我们生存的星球"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}